<p><strong>Beyond Work</strong></p>

<p>In a past life, I used to be a competitive quizzer. I had my 15 minutes on fame when I appeared on some <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-5pdjrdj0uA">nationally televised quiz shows</a> in my college days.</p>

